Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小姨子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,制片：madonna
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我先过去了\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个镇里出生 长大\N然后结婚组成家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我经营着10年前双亲留下来的建筑用品店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能就会在这里生活到死为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的年轻人都不知道羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,光天化日之下搂搂抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子都有了 真是不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小玲？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,社长 你认识?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，有点像\N她现在应该在东京
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:02:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老婆的妹妹小玲在东京结婚\N一年前生下孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一定很忙，不可能在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了\N喝吧，喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我住这里可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你公公和婆婆不用照顾了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们去了新森温泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,带了老婆去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你宝宝长得好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一岁的宝宝不可爱也不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃了晚饭，就一直睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个知趣的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,过分，姐姐怎么这么说妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在不是分居吗？\N分居哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？你老公回来不会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我暂时不想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我在怀孕生孩子，那么辛苦的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他居然和别的女人搞上了\N离婚才算是正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那你真的打算分手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,分手\N他都有女人了，大学女生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,估计带着她去哪里玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老公是社长，生活无忧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是个社长，只是开一家小店而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个家都是姊夫盖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是老是借钱出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次是店里，然后就是另外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说明姊夫是个很牢靠的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那户人家就这样处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的知道了\N那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姊夫没事吧\N没有什么花边新闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是一个很死板的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔只是去楼下小店喝下酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,和姐姐H吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要问了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最少一个月2次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,明石都12了\N要防着孩子，这个就不行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 回来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，工作完了就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小玲，欢迎\N打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,姊夫还是很忙啊\N小公司没办法，都要自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好像奶要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这时候应该是吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吸掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,宝宝不在身边就不行啊\N是啊，有点麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你就先在房间里面呆一下\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,挤奶器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,母乳都扔掉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，很浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有点涨涨的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,明石是喝母乳的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N这样啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,母乳营养好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候很麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很麻烦\N在电车上也要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧\N没有办法 他要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊…电车上太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这位妹妹…不知何时就已经是母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一位完整的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是面容依然是少女模样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,减肥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐你也不是瘦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，小下来了\N真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,之前没有这个，就用手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,突然想睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,最近好像没有睡好，老是想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐，能不能让我睡会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明石回来就会很吵的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，旁边有1个房间正好可以住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿姨过来住的房间\N可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,房间很明亮，我去收拾下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看着她我不禁发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这数十年来从没有过的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次希望没有娶妻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是钥匙\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了\N欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下就可以吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，能不能帮我叫下小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我动心了，我对妻子的妹妹动心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对妹妹动了非分之想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小玲，差不多该起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你姐姐让你起床
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,之后，小玲偶尔回来住在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不用照顾孩子白天的几小时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小玲在202房间里面度过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思，最近都没有什么好货色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我都改邪归正了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是我很有兴趣\N无线的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你可别搞出什么，乱拍女学生被警察给逮到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会给您添这种麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个摄影机真的那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然，据说警方都在用这家的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这里也有 个人使用设计的款式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还带有人体搜查拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只有人出现就会开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而且拍摄画面是超清晰的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,跟电视上一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,老是受您照顾，就借给您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要小心使用啊，都是些精密仪器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,两周内会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么社长您要用这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最近我家公寓里面好像有年轻男子出没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,公寓里面也有年轻的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有奇怪的人，我想通知警方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话就随便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以和警方解释了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个开关是这样的，关掉就不会拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是在倒追你嘛\N（录影画面）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是你自己不好，去找惹别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,活该啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你就好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,深夜，家里人都睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我一个人一直偷看着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一直偷窥着旁边房间的小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这好像是我每天的功课\N不…是乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错呢\N（播放画面）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.64,0:24:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.58,0:24:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.78,0:24:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是什么\N（播放画面）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.79,0:24:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你说房间？\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.79,0:24:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.59,0:24:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N他们都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.06,0:25:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了   不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.60,0:25:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是别人老婆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.75,0:25:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.55,0:25:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你那么美
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.62,0:25:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么把我魂都勾走了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.46,0:26:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.94,0:26:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.41,0:26:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.81,0:26:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么哪里，不要了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.48,0:26:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在乡下做这个会被到处说的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.57,0:26:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么，不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.04,0:26:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.78,0:26:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,奶还没有断啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.40,0:27:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.07,0:27:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.94,0:27:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要看 想要看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.74,0:27:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看出奶吗？ 有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.68,0:27:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.89,0:27:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.43,0:27:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我你要喝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.63,0:27:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂，你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.04,0:27:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.65,0:28:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈我要喝奶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.52,0:28:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢\N喝奶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.26,0:28:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要喝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.86,0:28:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喝什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.53,0:28:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.63,0:28:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要啊\N快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.57,0:29:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，飞溅
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.57,0:29:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  飞溅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.10,0:29:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.11,0:29:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,命中目标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.72,0:29:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当饭吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.19,0:29:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.93,0:29:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你当你是孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.40,0:29:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.55,0:29:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.16,0:29:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有点甜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.24,0:30:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.24,0:30:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.78,0:30:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.46,0:30:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.46,0:30:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.66,0:30:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不能在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.80,0:30:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就一下下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.02,0:31:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.23,0:31:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.50,0:31:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要挤
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.37,0:31:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.37,0:31:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是小孩子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.80,0:31:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.56,0:32:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.43,0:32:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,用奶干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.70,0:32:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.91,0:32:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.05,0:34:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也有奶味了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.25,0:34:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.57,0:35:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,该你了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.51,0:35:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.85,0:35:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.58,0:35:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,温暖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.12,0:36:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.85,0:36:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.19,0:36:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有射到
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好好瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.60,0:36:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.80,0:36:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.96,0:37:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.89,0:38:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.90,0:38:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那边 那边 有床
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.56,0:38:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这里才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.72,0:39:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.94,0:39:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.10,0:40:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.55,0:40:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.29,0:41:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.33,0:41:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,前面的我打不开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.40,0:41:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你的太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.01,0:41:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.97,0:42:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.18,0:42:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.19,0:42:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.59,0:42:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你老公哪个好？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.33,0:42:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.86,0:42:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是和老公做过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.00,0:42:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛问这
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.48,0:43:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.21,0:43:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.68,0:43:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,打开什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.28,0:43:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,打开脚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.77,0:43:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.71,0:43:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.59,0:43:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,爽不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.66,0:43:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.27,0:44:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.94,0:44:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.42,0:44:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.44,0:44:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒  去了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.65,0:45:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么那么喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.86,0:46:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.59,0:47:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.99,0:47:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.03,0:47:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.63,0:47:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.93,0:48:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给我奶
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.27,0:48:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.96,0:48:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.36,0:48:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.03,0:49:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.04,0:49:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.50,0:49:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那我多亲下你的乳房\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.77,0:49:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.98,0:49:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.44,0:49:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.78,0:49:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吧\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.91,0:49:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一下\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.18,0:49:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么一下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.72,0:49:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小气
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.39,0:49:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.39,0:49:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.99,0:49:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.46,0:49:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都不会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.73,0:49:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会这样的\N不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.54,0:49:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,反正不行\N那脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.54,0:49:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.01,0:49:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.34,0:49:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.35,0:51:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.11,0:51:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.18,0:51:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.90,0:52:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,餐巾纸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.51,0:52:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你真淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.25,0:52:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.46,0:52:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.59,0:52:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.46,0:52:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来得及吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.80,0:52:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.20,0:52:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可以洗澡么\N可以
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.01,0:53:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人和小玲分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.01,0:53:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小玲只是和他玩玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.42,0:53:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子的妹妹\N已经不再是以前的少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.49,0:53:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我更加欲求不满了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.62,0:53:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对妻子的妹妹欲求不满
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.90,0:54:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.37,0:54:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给我点洗发水
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.11,0:54:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.11,0:54:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还真的在出奶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.32,0:54:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.79,0:54:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.73,0:55:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.73,0:55:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.07,0:55:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.93,0:55:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.54,0:55:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.95,0:55:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.21,0:55:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.55,0:55:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不要说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.69,0:55:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小声点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.69,0:55:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,又没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.76,0:55:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.30,0:55:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢\N你会说出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.77,0:55:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没有关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.24,0:55:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,反正有姊夫在
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.38,0:55:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.45,0:55:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说一个月2次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.78,0:55:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.45,0:56:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N放进去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.92,0:56:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是正好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.39,0:56:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.13,0:56:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.80,0:56:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么正好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.93,0:56:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.60,0:56:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在我们这里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.47,0:56:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有这样的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.21,0:56:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.81,0:56:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.21,0:56:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.08,0:56:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,姊夫对声音什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.55,0:56:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,动作 很介意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.69,0:56:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,姊夫应该是很好玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.63,0:56:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.89,0:56:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢，好像没有这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.50,0:56:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？我看不是的\N就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.17,0:56:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我那个
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.30,0:56:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是不太喜欢这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.24,0:56:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.65,0:57:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(录像画面)
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.14,0:57:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(录像画面)
